name: Pendulum Xyz
desc: Target 2 cards in your Pendulum Zones; Special Summon them, but their effects are negated, and if you do, immediately after this effect resolves, Xyz Summon 1 Xyz Monster using only those 2 monsters as materials. You can treat the Level of 1 those materials as the same Level as the other's for this Xyz Summon. You can only activate 1 "Pendulum Xyz" per turn.
